column2: All I want to do now is have a drink.
I do not need to have a drink now.
It would be difficult to turn down a drink this minute.
Having a drink now would make things seem just perfect.
I want a drink so bad I can almost taste it.
Nothing would be better than having a drink right now.
If I had the chance to have a drink, I don’t think I would drink it.
I crave a drink right now.
